Below is a brief timeline of what you should aim to do in each week leading up to the submission of your report. **A table version is avaiable as PDF: download it [here](../assets/timeline.pdf).**

For technical help outside of practical sessions, please contact Gary Truong, our technical officer, via email -- the link is available on [Canvas](https://canvas.sydney.edu.au/courses/67437/pages/biology-experimental-design-and-analysis-beda).

**Jump to:** [Weeks 2--3](#wk2) | [Week 4](#wk4) | [Week 5](#wk5) | [Week 6](#wk6) | [Week 7](#wk7) | [Week 8](#wk8) | [Week 9](#wk9)

*Click on any week to expand or collapse its content.*

